data.description: Located in the prestigious Chapel Ridge golf course community this lot offers stunning views of the course from both the front and back. With a relatively flat terrain, this lot is ready for you to build your dream home. Enjoy the resort-style amenities that come with living in Chapel Ridge, including a pool, gym, playground, tennis, volleyball, and basketball courts, as well as a restaurant and bar. This is the perfect community for people who enjoy golf and outdoor activities. The property is conveniently located close to Chatham Park, which offers a variety of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Pittsboro is a charming town that boasts a rich history, natural beauty, and a thriving arts scene. With easy access to major highways, you can enjoy the best of both worlds – a peaceful and scenic retreat in Chapel Ridge and all the amenities of the city just a short drive away. Don't miss this opportunity to own apiece of paradise in Chapel Ridge. Adjoining lot is available.
